tags.name:
citation-element
An element dedicated to presenting and managing a correct citation on the web
both visually as well as semantically with simple inputs.
tags.jsDoc:
/**
 * `citation-element`
 * @customElement citation-element
 * An element dedicated to presenting and managing a correct citation on the web
 * both visually as well as semantically with simple inputs.
 * @demo demo/index.html
 */

attributes.name: display-method
attributes.description:
How to present the citation on the interface.
Can be popup, footnote, or default behavior which is visible
attributes.jsDoc:
/**
       * How to present the citation on the interface.
       * Can be popup, footnote, or default behavior which is visible
       */

attributes.name: creator
attributes.description: Person or group that owns / created the work.

attributes.name: source
attributes.description: Original Source of the work in question

attributes.name: license-name
attributes.description: License name, calculated or supplied by the end user if we don't have them.
